{"id":317725,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-上海235名民众联名要求联合国关注中国的人/","date":"2013-10-12T19:50:10Z","modified":"2013-10-12T19:50:10Z","title":"维权网 | 上海235名民众联名要求联合国关注中国的人权捍卫者（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员任泉报道）上海<span lang=\"EN-US\">235</span>名</span><span>维权</span><span>民</span><span>众</span><span>（只是冰山一角，多</span><span>数</span><span>是土地房屋被强</span><span>抢</span><span>掠</span><span>夺</span><span>后无家可</span><span>归</span><span>、无生活</span><span>来</span><span>源、无生命健康</span><span>权</span><span>、</span><span>诉</span><span>控无</span><span>门</span><span>。</span><span>专</span><span>制制度里的警察</span><span>们</span><span>不把</span><span>抢</span><span>劫</span><span>团伙</span><span>捉拿</span><span>归</span><span>案，而把受害者送</span><span>进</span><span>牢房，被</span><span>关</span><span>黑</span><span>监狱</span><span>、被强迫失踪、甚至被自</span><span>杀</span><span>）</span><span>联</span><span>名，</span><span>强烈要求</span><span>联</span><span>合</span><span>国人权理事会为</span><span>上海</span><span>维权</span><span>人士</span><span>陈</span><span>建芳“被阻止出境”和北京</span><span>维权</span><span>人士曹</span><span>顺</span><span>利“被阻止出境强迫失踪”</span><span> 事件进行</span><span>紧</span><span>急呼吁，必须的</span><span>调查</span><span>和救助行</span><span>动，并对</span><span>案件</span><span>发</span><span>布公</span><span>开声</span><span>明（</span><span>还应调查</span><span>追究侵</span><span>权</span><span>者的法律</span><span>责</span><span>任）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今年<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>日，上海</span><span>维权</span><span>人士</span><span>陈</span><span>建芳</span><span>和北京</span><span>维权</span><span>人士曹</span><span>顺</span><span>利</span><span>应</span><span>“</span><span>国际</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>服</span><span>务</span><span>”邀</span><span>请</span><span>前往瑞士日</span><span>内</span><span>瓦</span><span>参</span><span>加人</span><span>权</span><span>培</span><span>训</span><span>和</span><span>观</span><span>摩</span><span>联</span><span>合</span><span>国</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>机制</span><span>运</span><span>作。</span><span>陈</span><span>建芳</span><span>带</span><span>着</span><span>护</span><span>照、瑞士</span><span>签证</span><span>、登机牌等有效</span><span>证</span><span>件在广州白云机</span><span>场</span><span>登机时被广州白云出入境</span><span>边</span><span>防</span><span>检查</span><span>站无任何手</span><span>续</span><span>和理由阻止出境。</span><span>她</span><span>在广州白云机</span><span>场</span><span>捍</span><span>卫</span><span>出</span><span>国权</span><span>的第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>天得知母</span><span>亲</span><span>在上海被</span><span>当</span><span>局恐</span><span>吓</span><span>突</span><span>发</span><span>心</span><span>脏</span><span>病（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span>日</span><span>医</span><span>院出具《病危通知</span><span>书</span><span>》），</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日中午</span><span>约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分回到上海，下了</span><span>飞</span><span>机台</span><span>阶即</span><span>被守候在此的市</span><span>国</span><span>保截走</span><span>关</span><span>押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>个</span><span>小</span><span>时</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>曹</span><span>顺</span><span>利在北京机</span><span>场</span><span>登机被强迫失踪，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span>日有消息</span><span>称</span><span>“被刑事拘留”</span><span>关</span><span>押在北京市第一看守所，但是曹</span><span>顺</span><span>利家</span><span>属</span><span>至今未收到法律文</span><span>书</span><span>，去派出所</span><span>查问</span><span>，得到回答：“不知道”。</span><span> 曹</span><span>顺</span><span>利至今仍然</span><span>处</span><span>于被失踪</span><span>状态</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海<span lang=\"EN-US\">235</span>名</span><span>维权</span><span>民</span><span>众</span><span>强烈要求中共</span><span>当</span><span>局立即</span><span>还</span><span>曹</span><span>顺</span><span>利人身自由，放行曹</span><span>顺</span><span>利和</span><span>陈</span><span>建芳等人</span><span>权</span><span>捍</span><span>卫</span><span>者去</span><span>联</span><span>合</span><span>国参</span><span>加旁听</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span>日</span><span>对</span><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>的普遍定期</span><span>审议</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今年<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>日</span><span>联</span><span>合</span><span>国举</span><span>行人</span><span>权</span><span>理事</span><span>会</span><span>成</span><span>员选举</span><span>，</span><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>政府在今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span>份</span><span>已宣布</span><span>参选</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2014 </span><span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016 </span>年人</span><span>权</span><span>理事</span><span>会</span><span>成</span><span>员</span><span>，</span><span>并</span><span>向</span><span>联</span><span>大主席</span><span>递</span><span>交了“自愿承</span><span>诺</span><span>”：“推</span><span>动并</span><span>保</span><span>护</span><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>人民的人</span><span>权</span><span>和基本自由”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>政府承</span><span>诺</span><span>：“中</span><span>国</span><span>政府尊重人</span><span>权</span><span>普遍性原</span><span>则</span><span>，</span><span>为</span><span>促</span><span>进</span><span>和保</span><span>护</span><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>人民的人</span><span>权</span><span>和基本自由作出了不懈努力。中</span><span>国认真</span><span>履行相</span><span>关国际</span><span>人</span><span>权条约义务</span><span>，</span><span>与联</span><span>合</span><span>国</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>机制合作，</span><span>并</span><span>建</span><span>设</span><span>性</span><span>参与</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>理事</span><span>会</span><span>的体制</span><span>建</span><span>设</span><span>、普遍定期</span><span>审议</span><span>机制和人</span><span>权</span><span>理事</span><span>会</span><span>所有</span><span>项</span><span>目的</span><span>审议</span><span>工作。中</span><span>国</span><span>通</span><span>过</span><span>自己的努力，</span><span>帮</span><span>助促</span><span>进国际</span><span>人</span><span>权领</span><span>域的建</span><span>设</span><span>性</span><span>对话</span><span>和合作。中</span><span>国</span><span>政府相信，中</span><span>国</span><span>担任人</span><span>权</span><span>理事</span><span>会</span><span>成</span><span>员将</span><span>有助于人</span><span>权</span><span>理事</span><span>会</span><span>促</span><span>进</span><span>和保</span><span>护</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>的崇高事</span><span>业</span><span>。</span><span>随</span><span>信附上中</span><span>国参选</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>理事</span><span>会</span><span>成</span><span>员</span><span>的</span><span>备</span><span>忘</span><span>录</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>见</span><span>附件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span>”。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海<span lang=\"EN-US\">235</span>名</span><span>维权</span><span>民</span><span>众</span><span>表示：把所有被</span><span>关</span><span>押的民主人士、</span><span>异见</span><span>人士、</span><span>维权</span><span>律</span><span>师</span><span>和</span><span>维权访</span><span>民、信仰者全部无罪</span><span>释</span><span>放，</span><span>并给</span><span>予</span><span>国</span><span>家</span><span>赔偿</span><span>。</span><span>不然“承</span><span>诺</span><span>”不攻自破，“承</span><span>诺</span><span>”</span><span>骗</span><span>不了中</span><span>国</span><span>人，只能</span><span>骗</span><span>外</span><span>国</span><span>人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家一致</span><span>认为</span><span>：中</span><span>国没</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>，是</span><span>联</span><span>合</span><span>国</span><span>的</span><span>责</span><span>任，</span><span>联</span><span>合</span><span>国</span><span>不</span><span>该</span><span>听信</span><span>谎</span><span>言。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" t